WEBVTT

00:08.967 --> 00:12.711
Well, it was different.
I, uh, was on the run, Al.

00:13.472 --> 00:14.633
From what?

00:15.807 --> 00:17.327
- What were you on the run...
- People.

00:19.353 --> 00:20.353
It was people.

00:21.188 --> 00:22.645
See, somebody helped me.

00:25.359 --> 00:26.725
That's what this is all about.

00:28.000 --> 00:34.074
Advertise your product or brand here
